BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.broadbandreports.com/shownews/63347"&gt;Google glitched&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABroadband%20News"&gt;Broadband News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 7, 2005
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//www.gigaom.com/2005/05/07/google-hacked/"&gt;Google Hacked? No DNS Glitch says Google&lt;/a&gt; Om Malik's Broadband Blog, Saturday, May 7 at 3:11 PM
