BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.outsidethebeltway.com/archives/10403"&gt;GoogleNews Refinement Plan Could Oust Blogs&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AOutsideTheBeltway.com"&gt;OutsideTheBeltway.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 4, 2005
BULLET::::- Rich Ord. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.webpronews.com/news/ebusinessnews/wpn-45-20050503GoogleNewsPatentApplicationFullText.html"&gt;Google News Patent Application - Full Text&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWebProNews.com"&gt;WebProNews.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 3, 2005
BULLET::::- Barry Fox. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.newscientist.com/channel/info-tech/mg18624975.900"&gt;Google searches for quality not quantity&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANewScientist.com"&gt;NewScientist.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, April 30, 2005

