BULLET::::- STEVE LAWRENCE, Associated Press Writer. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/news%3Ftmpl%3Dstory%26amp%3Bu%3D/ap/20050511/ap_on_re_us/gay_marriage_california"&gt;Calif. Groups Push Gay Marriage Ban&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AYahoo%21"&gt;Yahoo!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 11, 2005
BULLET::::- CNSNews.com. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.townhall.com/news/politics/200505/CUL20050511a.shtml"&gt;Conservative Group Writing California Marriage Amendment&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ATownhall.com"&gt;Townhall.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 11, 2005

</ul>
