BULLET::::- &lt;a href="http%3A//english.aljazeera.net/NR/exeres/8362939C-770A-4A62-95FB-416DA1B4AE7C.htm"&gt;Brazil summit policies at odds with US&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAlJazeera"&gt;AlJazeera&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; , May 11, 2005.

</ul>


