BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.ilo.org/public/english/bureau/inf/pr/2005/22.htm"&gt;ILO releases major new study on forced labour&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AILO"&gt;ILO&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;,
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.ilo.org/dyn/declaris/DECLARATIONWEB.DOWNLOAD_BLOB%3FVar_DocumentID%3D2841"&gt;Special Action to combat Forced Labour&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AILO"&gt;ILO&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;,

</ul>
