BULLET::::- Barry Schweid. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20050512/ap_on_go_co/un_ambassador"&gt;Voinovich Slams Bolton but OKs Senate Vote&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 12, 2005

