BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.respectcoalition.org/%3Fite%3D779"&gt;Galloway again rebuts Senate lies&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ARESPECT"&gt;RESPECT&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 12, 2005
BULLET::::- Kim Pilling and Victoria Ward, PA. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.scotsman.com/latest.cfm%3Fid%3D4545296"&gt;Galloway Gets U.S. Invite Amid New Iraq Oil Row&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Scotsman"&gt;The Scotsman&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 12, 2005
