BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.rte.ie/business/2005/0512/inflation.html"&gt;Annual inflation creeps up to 2.2% in April&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ARTE%20News"&gt;RTE News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 12, 2005
