<ul>
BULLET::::- Ronen Zvulun. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20050512/ts_nm/mideast_dc"&gt;Gaza settlers protest on Israel's Independence Day&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 12, 2005

</ul>


