BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20050514/ts_nm/mexico_usa_dc"&gt;Mexico's Fox toughens talk on U.S. immigration law&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 14, 2005
BULLET::::- &lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUPI"&gt;UPI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//washingtontimes.com/upi-breaking/20050513-074358-4758r.htm"&gt;Mexico: Fox to protest immigration law&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Times"&gt;Washington Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 13, 2005

</ul>


