BULLET::::- Shamil Baigin. "&lt;a href="http%3A//abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory%3Fid%3D757124"&gt;Uzbek president blames Islamic group for violence&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AABC%20News%20%28US%29"&gt;ABC News (US)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 14, 2005
</ul>
 


