BULLET::::- David Morgan. "&lt;a href="http%3A//story.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20050515/ts_nm/religion_afghan_newsweek_dc"&gt;Newsweek says Koran desecration report is wrong&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters%20via%20Yahoo%21%20News"&gt;Reuters via Yahoo! News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 15, 2005
