BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk./1/hi/technology/4544547.stm"&gt;Microsoft offers security service&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News"&gt;BBC News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 13, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//moneyplans.net/frontend2-verify-6972.html"&gt;Microsoft plans to release security services&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMoney%20Plans"&gt;Money Plans&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 16, 2005
