BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/music/4554035.stm"&gt;Kylie Minogue has breast cancer&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News"&gt;BBC News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 17, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//seven.com.au/news/entertainment/81571"&gt;Kylie diagnosed with breast cancer&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASeven%20Network"&gt;Seven Network&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 17, 2005
</ul>
 


