BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//ilmessaggero.caltanet.it/index.php%3Fdata%3D20050516%26amp%3Bediz%3D01_NAZIONALE%26amp%3Bgrpag%3Dpagine/SPORT%26amp%3Bpag%3D0%26amp%3Bps%3D0%26amp%3Bvis%3DG%26amp%3Btt%3D"&gt;Never again like this&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AIl%20Messaggero"&gt;Il Messaggero&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 17, 2005
