BULLET::::- Mihai Istrate. "&lt;a href="http%3A//daily-news.ro/article_detail.php%3Fidarticle%3D10975"&gt;New Air France flight to Bucharest&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABucharest%20Daily%20News"&gt;Bucharest Daily News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 18, 2005

</ul>


