BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Associated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.tuscaloosanews.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article%3FAID%3D/20050518/APN/505180726"&gt;Tropical Storm Adrian in Pacific, heading for Caribbean&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ATuscaloosa%20News"&gt;Tuscaloosa News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 18, 2005
