BULLET::::- Kevin Krolicki and Alexandria Sage. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.reuters.com/newsArticle.jhtml%3Ftype%3DpoliticsNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D8535923"&gt;'We're all Angelenos' says L.A.'s Latino mayor&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Wed May 18, 2005 06:49 PM ET
