BULLET::::- Ben Charny. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.zdnet.com/2100-1035_22-5713446.html%3Ftag%3Dnl"&gt;FCC requires VoIP to clean up its 911 act&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AZDNet"&gt;ZDNet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 20, 2005
BULLET::::- Paul Davidson. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.usatoday.com/tech/news/techpolicy/2005-05-19-internet-phones-911_x.htm"&gt;VoIP systems must offer full 911 services&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUSA%20Today"&gt;USA Today&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 20, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.fcc.gov/"&gt;FCC news release page&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AFCC"&gt;FCC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 20, 2005

</ul>
