BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.iht.com/articles/2005/05/22/asia/web.0522mongolia.php"&gt;Mongolia votes for new president&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 21, 2005
