BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.fena.ba/uk/vijest.html%3Ffena_id%3DFSA264770%26amp%3Brubrika%3DES"&gt;SARAJEVO: MARKING OF TITO’S BIRTHDAY&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AFENA%20News"&gt;FENA News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 25, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.vecernji-list.hr/newsroom/zanimljivosti/293714/index.do"&gt;Šest tisuća ljudi slavilo rođendan Josipa Broza&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AVecernji%20List"&gt;Vecernji List&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 22, 2005
