<ul>
BULLET::::- Aida Sultanova. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.businessweek.com/ap/financialnews/D8AABN4G0.htm%3Fcampaign_id%3Dapn_home_down"&gt;First pipeline from Caspian Sea opened&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABusiness%20Week%20Online"&gt;Business Week Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 25, 2005

