<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.monstersandcritics.com/southamerica/article_1001210.php/Brazil_Lula_allies_back_corruption_probe"&gt;Brazil: Lula allies back corruption probe&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AUnited%20Press%20International"&gt;United Press International&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 19, 2005

