BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.finfacts.com/irelandbusinessnews/publish/article_10001965.shtml"&gt;Ryanair celebrates 20th birthday with seat sale&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AFinfacts.com"&gt;Finfacts.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 26, 2005
