BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.sharecast.com/cgi-bin/sharecast/story.cgi%3Fstory_id%3D487180"&gt;Scottish Radio snaps up Irish minnow&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AShareCast"&gt;ShareCast&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 31, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.forbes.com/business/feeds/afx/2005/05/31/afx2064556.html"&gt;Scottish Radio to buy Donegal Highland Radio for around 7 mln eur&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AForbes"&gt;Forbes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 31, 2005
