BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.forbes.com/home/feeds/afx/2005/05/30/afx2063461.html"&gt;SKorea's Samsung Electronics produces first 4-gigabit NAND flash memory&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AForbes"&gt;Forbes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 1, 2005
BULLET::::- Graeme Wearden. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.zdnet.co.uk/hardware/storage/0%2C39020366%2C39201341%2C00.htm"&gt;Samsung starts mass production of 70nm flash&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AZDNet"&gt;ZDNet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 1, 2005
BULLET::::- Paul Kallender. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.techworld.com/storage/news/index.cfm%3FNewsID%3D3761"&gt;Samsung moves to 70nm Flash&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ATechworld"&gt;Techworld&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 31, 2005
