BULLET::::- Jackie Shaken. "&lt;a href="http%3A//216.55.181.228/videos/cnn053105III.wmv"&gt;Inside the Blogs (video)&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, May 31, 2005

