BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.irinnews.org/report.asp%3FReportID%3D47435"&gt;ZIMBABWE: Human rights body files for stay of forced evictions&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AIRIN%20news"&gt;IRIN news&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 1, 2005
