BULLET::::- Robert Burns. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/s/ap/guantanamo_bay_quran"&gt;U.S.: Gitmo Quran Was Splashed With Urine&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 4, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/4608949.stm"&gt;US Guantanamo guard kicked Koran&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABBC%20News"&gt;BBC News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 4, 2005
BULLET::::- Oliver Moore. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20050604.wkoran0604/BNStory/International/"&gt;U.S. military finds abuse of Koran&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AGlobe%20and%20Mail"&gt;Globe and Mail&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 4, 2005
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2005/US/06/03/guantanamo.quran/index.html"&gt;Detainees, not soldiers, flushed Quran&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 4, 2005

